bilingual.target: 木头是一种常见的固体材料。

bilingual.source: This piece of solid metal is very heavy.
This piece of solid chocolate is delicious.
bilingual.target: 这块固体巧克力很好吃。

bilingual.source: The ice cube is a solid at room temperature.
bilingual.target: 冰块在室温下是固体的。

bilingual.source: Water turns into a solid below zero degrees.
bilingual.target: 水在零度以下会变成固体。
过滤可以去除大部分悬浮固体。

bilingual.source: Suspended solid in water can affect its quality.
bilingual.target: 水中的悬浮固体会影响水质。

bilingual.source: He built a solid wall to protect his garden.
bilingual.target: 他建了一堵固体的墙来保护他的花园。

bilingual.source: She prefers solid furniture because it lasts longer.
bilingual.target: 她更喜欢固体的家具，因为它更耐用。

list.abstract: 全球领先的高可用实时数据库解决方案提供商Solid™ Information Technology。 Solid公司于1992年在芬兰首都赫尔辛基成立，致力于提供创新性的数据管理解决方案，使网络用户可以随时随地获取数据，就如同拨打电话时可以听到电话铃声一样。 Solid™ Information Technologysolid的DB关系数据库为各个行业的业务系统提供高性能、永不间断的数据管理平台，已经被全球超过300 万个关键任务系统所采用， 其高性能、高可靠性经过了十多年的应用检验，并且在电信、金融等行业的各种应用中积累了丰富的成功经验。

yingyinNormal.en: The only way to the internal mechanics was through solid titanium.
yingyinNormal.zh: 唯一能进入导弹内部结构的方法是穿过钛固体。

yingyinNormal.en: A couple things. Now that she eats solid food, she poops around the clock. And watch out for your hair because she likes to grab it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有几件事，现在她会吃固体食物了，所以会按时排便，还有小心你的头发，因为她喜欢抓。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, dinner's ready. Good game. Yeah.Yeah. Solid effort. Solid effort.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，晚餐准备好了。好吧。真的很精彩。

yingyinNormal.en: We're booked solid for the next month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们下个月全部都被订满了。

yingyinNormal.en: You're both confident that this is rock solid?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们确定是铁板钉钉吗？

yingyinNormal.en: We have solid information, an attack is coming.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可靠情报显示袭击就在眼前。

yingyinNormal.en: If not removed, to solid ice will you freeze, forever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果不拿开的话这块冰，它会冰冻你，直到永远。

yingyinNormal.en: Solid information, a secret terrorist organization is planning an attack.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可靠情报，秘密恐怖组织正在策划一场袭击。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, while also getting in a solid dig at you. Pretty efficient?
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，我还同时好好挖苦了你一番，这才叫一石二鸟。

yingyinNormal.en: You okay? He gave me an F. That's nuts. You're a solid D Student.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没事吧？他给我打了个F。那真是太离谱了，你向来稳稳的都是D啊。

yingyinNormal.en: And that's not a fluke. It keeps up the solid pace of job creation we've seen all year long.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是侥幸而来的，这是我们整年以来看到的持续稳定的发展速度。

yingyinNormal.en: Hopefully every day brings solid ground. But with everything you know, are you jumping or what?
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许接下来的每一天你都可以脚踏实地，不过你再仔细考虑一下，你确定要跳下去吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And when I finally set foot back on solid ground, the first thing I heard was that goddamn voice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我终于再次踏上坚实的大地，第一个听到的就是那该死的声音。

yingyinNormal.en: Try not to get too righteous and listen a little. Okay, fine. Who is this guy? A real solid-gold asshole.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽量别太正义，听着点。好吧，这位是谁？一个十足的混蛋。

yingyinNormal.en: So...Says you. ...you're convinced the underlying mortgages in these bonds are solid loans. That is our opinion, yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么… 口说无凭。你确信这些债券对应的房贷是可靠的吗？根据我们公司的观点，是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, that's right. Institutions treat these CDOs like they're as solid as treasury bonds, and they're going to zero.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，就是这样，各大机构对于担保债务凭证的态度就好像他们如国库券一般稳健，但他们就要坍塌了。

yingyinNormal.en: Here is a present for you. An antique clock. Woo. It's made of solid plastic. Thank you. But why is there a party for me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个是我们给你的礼物！他是一个古董钟羚羊夫人。哦。他其实是一个塑料组成的。谢谢你们，但是为什么要给我举办派对呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Here is a present for you. An antique clock. Woo. It's made of solid plastic. Thank you. But why is there a party for me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个是我们给你的礼物！他是一个古董钟羚羊夫人。哦。他其实是一个塑料组成的。谢谢你们，但是为什么要给我举办派对呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Is it solid gold? Gilded steel. You're not eating. Why is no one eating? My wife wastes away and my brother starves himself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是纯金的吗？精钢镀金，你不吃东西，为什么所有人都不吃东西？我老婆日渐消瘦，我哥哥绝食挨饿。

yingyinNormal.en: So I ran away, crossed the shining sea. And when I finally set foot back on solid ground, the first thing I heard was that voice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我逃跑了，越过大洋到达彼岸，当我终于踏上坚实的大地，第一个听到的就是那该死的声音。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: strongly built or made of strong materials

word_usage.usage: solid作“固体的”、“实心的”或 “连续的”解时，无比较级和最高级形式；当表示其他意思，如“可靠的”时，solid只有最高级，无比较级。
